Aerial perspective in painting: Two Monkeys, Bird Nester-dark foreground, Climax: Magpie on Gallows. Pointillistic technique in painting of trees, e.g. Tower of Babel. My 2nd ed., pl. 57, 59, 62, 96. The Haymaking (my pls. 93, 94, 95 in 2nd.ed.)
